@host = https://localhost:7177

### Create a product that FAILS validation (name too short, price 0) -> 400 + errors
POST {{host}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ab",
  "description": "",
  "price": 0
}

### Create a valid product -> 201 Created
POST {{host}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Standing Desk",
  "description": "Electric height-adjustable desk",
  "price": 399.99
}

### List all products
GET {{host}}/products
